reviewText: Excellent work out for the total gym. Lots of room to advance. Todd knows how to motivate too.

Bought the three dvd series to use with my Total Trainer by Bayou.  This third dvd in the series is awesome.  You really get a great workout and Durkin is inspiring.  The results have been noticeable.  Glad I bought it.  It is like having a five star trainer ready whenever you want to work out.

I enjoy the intensity of the workout.  It allows one to stay motivated and on task getting the most out of the time you are working.  be prepared to work hard and get the results.  By the end of the workout I am feeling great, sweating a lot and ready to meet the day.
Check it out!
